<% layout("layouts/boilerplate") %>

<section class="static-page">
  <div class="static-header reveal-on-scroll">
    <p class="eyebrow"><i class="fa-solid fa-compass"></i> Our Story</p>
    <h1>About WanderLust</h1>
    <p class="static-lead">Where AI-powered travel planning meets premium accommodation discovery.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="static-content reveal-on-scroll">
    <h2><i class="fa-solid fa-globe"></i> What is WanderLust?</h2>
    <p>
      WanderLust is a modern travel platform that combines the best of two worlds: discovering
      premium accommodations across the globe and planning complete travel itineraries powered
      by artificial intelligence. Whether you're a solo backpacker, a couple seeking a romantic
      getaway, or a family planning an adventure, WanderLust has you covered.
    </p>

    <div class="about-features">
      <div class="about-feature reveal-on-scroll">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-house-chimney"></i>
        <h3>Accommodation Discovery</h3>
        <p>Browse curated homes, villas, cabins, and city apartments from hosts worldwide.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-feature reveal-on-scroll">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-wand-magic-sparkles"></i>
        <h3>AI Travel Planner</h3>
        <p>Generate personalized day-by-day itineraries tailored to your budget and style.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-feature reveal-on-scroll">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-file-pdf"></i>
        <h3>PDF Export</h3>
        <p>Download your complete itinerary as a PDF to share or use offline.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-feature reveal-on-scroll">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-map-location-dot"></i>
        <h3>Interactive Maps</h3>
        <p>Explore listing locations with Mapbox-powered interactive maps.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-feature reveal-on-scroll">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i>
        <h3>Reviews & Ratings</h3>
        <p>Read authentic reviews from fellow travelers before booking.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-feature reveal-on-scroll">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-shield-halved"></i>
        <h3>Secure & Trusted</h3>
        <p>Secure authentication, verified hosts, and protected user data.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2><i class="fa-solid fa-wand-magic-sparkles"></i> AI-Powered Planning</h2>
    <p>
      Our AI Planner uses Google Gemini to analyze your preferences — destination, budget tier,
      travel style, interests, and dietary needs — and generates a comprehensive itinerary
      covering 15+ sections including daily plans, budget breakdowns, food recommendations,
      packing checklists, hidden gems, photo spots, and emergency information.
    </p>
    <p>
      After generating your itinerary, WanderLust automatically suggests matching accommodations
      from our listing database, creating a seamless connection between planning and booking.
    </p>

    <h2><i class="fa-solid fa-people-group"></i> Built for Travelers</h2>
    <p>
      WanderLust was built with a focus on real usability. The platform is fully responsive,
      works beautifully on mobile and desktop, and follows modern web standards. Every feature
      — from listing search and filtering to AI itinerary generation and trip saving — is
      designed to make travel planning effortless and enjoyable.
    </p>

    <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 2.5rem;">
      <a href="/planner" class="btn btn-primary app-btn btn-lg">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-wand-magic-sparkles"></i> Try the AI Planner
      </a>
      <a href="/listings" class="btn btn-outline-dark app-btn btn-lg ms-2">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-compass"></i> Explore Stays
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
